NOTICE AND CLAIM OF LIEN
Notice is hereby given of assessment of a lien by the City of Glendale upon the following described real
property of the following utility customer for Sewer, water, taxes, refuse and late charges in the amount of
$892.91 as of 09/01/2021, plus service charges in the amount of 1.5% per month or part thereof from and
after the above date, and the filing and postage fees listed below.
UTILITY CUSTOMER:
Ethan Nightengale
LEGAL DESCRIPTION:
Description: Windsor Square Estates
MCR# 24914
Lot# 194
APN: 148-20-338
Service Address: 8513 N. 53rd Ave.
Glendale, AZ 85302
This assessment is made pursuant to Glendale City Code Sec. 33-81, and constitutes a lien in favor of the
City of Glendale upon said Real properties listed in addition to any other real property not specified on
this lien. This notice and claim of lien is filed for delinquent and past-due utility billings. Applicable
filing fee will be applied.
James A. Gruber
Deputy City Attorney
STATE OF ARIZONA
County of Maricopa
